	Beer wash    
	 London, March 24 (PTI): Actress Catherine Zeta-Jones prefers to use honey and beer to wash her hair as it leaves them shining.      
	Jones said she uses a concoction of products to maintain her luscious locks and glowing skin, reports OK! magazine. I keep my skin clear by applying a mixture of honey and salt all over my body to moisturise. I also condition my hair with honey and beer, she said.
                                                                                                                                                      
